{"tid":1873444,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"HKUSpace夾學生去新加坡，唔比退錢","createTime":"2020-02-10T16:16:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T17:58:56.000Z","uid":68125,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"61a5abe8228fda9abf2ed5d572bd87b7d5b3455a","tid":1873444,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:16:53.000Z","msg":"內容轉自K&rsquo;s Aviation <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/495667450636161/posts/1231105723758993/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F495667450636161%2Fposts%2F1231105723758993%2F&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4QfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=94580977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/495667450636161/posts/1231105723758993/</a><br />\n<br />\n有 HKUSPACE Aviation學生向我們表示，自二月武漢肺炎於新加坡情況惡化以來，校方並沒有打算取消新加坡航空展 遊學團，為將收入袋袋平安並將學生健康置之度外，所以想我們代為公開。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，是次有近八十人參加有關五日四夜遊學團，而校方不希望跟Pacific Arena Limited進行退款。為確保校方免退款及不用負責 #武漢肺炎 潛在風險，強行要求學生選擇不退款退團或要求學生簽免責聲明，確認得悉潛在風險，變相要求學生自行承擔武漢肺炎之健康風險。<br />\n<br />\n連我們都選擇不前往新加坡航空展及於網站申請退款，為何要學生無退款權利下，校方要求學生簽免責聲明呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uOLrF1O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuOLrF1O.jpg&h=68fb4f1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K0xd5tt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK0xd5tt.jpg&h=9582c394&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/78EgiOu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F78EgiOu.jpg&h=df995b2d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UBE79U9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUBE79U9.jpg&h=b4f74e2a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4C0nYOv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4C0nYOv.jpg&h=df1df06b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81672c68b2c55620283444a3645cfeb785bf352c","tid":1873444,"uid":168020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"